OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDon't use refund firms to  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fclaim tax rebates, says    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FWhich?                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Using a company to help you claim a tax
OL,6, rebate could end up costing you        
OL,7, hundreds of pounds extra according to  
OL,8, consumer group Which?                  
OL,10,FDozens of firms online offer to help   
OL,11,Fcustomers claim back tax they're owed  
OL,12,Fby HM Revenue & Customs, for example,  
OL,13,Ffor the Marriage Allowance.            
OL,15,FBut these third-party firms charge fees
OL,16,Fand take a percentage of the tax claim.
OL,18,FWhich? says most people are much better
OL,19,Foff going straight to HMRC themselves  
OL,20,Fto avoid "unnecessary bills".          
